description:
Chloë Grace Moretz [Kick-Ass, Carrie, Suspiria, Tom and Jerry] talks with Anna about her new film Tom and Jerry, not quite living in Los Angeles, fight training, sharing M&Ms, ghosts, aliens, friend groups, patriotism, going back to school, life in the circus, Frederick Douglass, the importance of an orange and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined by Dr. Lisa Marie Bobby, the founder and clinical director of Growing Self Counseling and Coaching.

Learn more about Dr. Bobby at www.growingself.com and check out her podcast The Love, Happiness and Success Podcast
